        "title": "Meet API",
        "description": "Move your app forward with the Meet API\n\n## API Success Code\n\nCode  | HTTP Code | Message\n----- | --------- | --------\n200001 | 200 | You can go to check your email\n200002 | 200 | Account validation success\n200003 | 200 | Signin success\n200004 | 200 | Create a new post successfully\n200005 | 200 | You have allowed to post articles\n200006 | 200 | Get some articles\n\n\n## API Error Code - 400\n\nError Code  | HTTP Code | Message\n------| --- | -----------------------------------\n401001 | 401 | Email or password is not valid\n401002 | 401 | Token is not valid or expired\n401003 | 401 | Email token is not valid or expired\n401004 | 401 | No Authorization header found\n401004 | 401 | Invalid Token\n403001 | 403 | The email has already been registered in social account\n403002 | 403 | The email has already been registered\n403003 | 403 | You can't repeatly post article in 3 minutes\n404001 | 404 | Your email account is not activated\n404002 | 404 | We could not find your account\n422001 | 422 | Length of password must >= 6\n\n## API Error Code - 500\n\nError Code  | HTTP Code | Message\n------| --- | -----------------------------------    \n500001 | 500 | Bcrypt error\n500002 | 500 | Your data is bad and you should feel bad\n503001 | 503 | SMTP server unavailable to verify\n503002 | 503 | SMTP server unavailable to send\n\n ## API Error Code - Bonus\n \nError Code  | HTTP Code | Message\n------| --- | -----------------------------------    \n-1 | Unknow | Unknow\n",
